Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_tx_col_attempt

AGL_GMX_TX_COL_ATTEMPT = Packet TX collision attempts before dropping frame

Notes: Additionally reset when both MIX0/1_CTL[RESET] are set to 1.
